]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>🤖 多智能体图推理实战指南</title><link>https://radar.huadongpeng.com/posts/ai-frontier/deep-dive-2026-05-11/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 07:53:02 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://radar.huadongpeng.com/posts/ai-frontier/deep-dive-2026-05-11/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="一技术原理白盒拆解"&gt;一、技术原理白盒拆解&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;通俗解释&lt;/strong&gt;：想象一个团队分工解题——有人负责扫一眼全局，有人专门计算局部路径，最后汇总答案。GraphDC把这种模式应用在图算法上，通过“分治-协调”提升推理准确性。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;技术原理&lt;/strong&gt;：核心机制是Divide-and-Conquer Multi-Agent。首先，一个“分解决略智能体”将大图拆成若干子图；然后，多个“子图求解智能体”并行处理（使用LLM推理）；最后，“合并智能体”整合结果。与传统单LLM直接推理相比，这种结构减少了上下文长度爆炸和混淆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;性能对比表&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;维度&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;GraphDC&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;单LLM直接推理&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;专业图算法库（如NetworkX）&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;准确率（8节点图）&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;89%&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;62%&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;100%&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;成本（每100次）&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;$0.03（GPT-4o-mini）&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;$0.06（GPT-4o）&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;免费（计算资源）&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;灵活性&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;支持任意图结构零样本&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;需提示工程&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;需编程实现&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;响应时间&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;3-5秒&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;1-2秒&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&amp;lt;0.01秒&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GraphDC在性能与成本之间取得平衡：接近专业算法准确率，但无需人工编码，适合快速原型。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="二替代人工的量化分析"&gt;二、替代人工的量化分析&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;生成业务依赖关系图并分析关键路径&lt;/strong&gt;：项目经理通常人工耗时2天，成本$800。用GraphDC自动化，耗时15分钟，成本&amp;lt;$0.01。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;对知识图谱查询进行推理（多跳关系）&lt;/strong&gt;：数据科学家每次查询耗时4小时（含编写复杂SPARQL），自动化后10秒，成本$0.005。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;代码结构分析—寻找循环依赖&lt;/strong&gt;：开发人员手动审查大型代码库耗时8小时/次，自动化后5分钟，节省$400。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;社交网络影响力传播路径预测&lt;/strong&gt;：市场分析师人工多轮计算耗时6小时，自动化后2分钟，成本$0.002。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;供应链路径优化（初步方案）&lt;/strong&gt;：运营团队需要3天制定备选路径，自动化后20分钟，节省$1200。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="三easton-实战接入方案核心章节500字"&gt;三、Easton 实战接入方案（核心章节，≥500字）&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本方案使用GraphDC论文核心思路，基于GPT-4o-mini实现轻量级多智能体图推理。所有组件免费使用，仅需OpenAI API（或使用本地模型）。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# graphdc_mini.py - Zero-cost Multi-Agent Graph Reasoning&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; os
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; json
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; logging
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; typing &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; Dict, List, Any
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; openai &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# pip install openai&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;logging&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;basicConfig(level&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;logging&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;INFO, format&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;%(asctime)s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;%(levelname)s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;%(message)s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;logger &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; logging&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;getLogger(__name__)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 配置 - 设置为你的OpenAI API Key，或使用免费模型如Ollama&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;os&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;environ[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;OPENAI_API_KEY&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;your-api-key-here&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 替换为实际Key&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;client &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; openai&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;OpenAI()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;llm_call&lt;/span&gt;(prompt: str, model: str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;gpt-4o-mini&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, temperature: float &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0.0&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; str:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;安全调用LLM，含错误处理&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; response &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; client&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;chat&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;completions&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;create(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; model&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;model,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; messages&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;[{&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;role&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;user&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;content&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: prompt}],
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; temperature&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;temperature,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; max_tokens&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; )
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; response&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;choices[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;message&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;content&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;strip()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;except&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Exception&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; e:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; logger&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;error(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;LLM call failed: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;e&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;ERROR: LLM call failed&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;decompose_graph&lt;/span&gt;(graph_desc: str) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; List[str]:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;智能体1：将图分解为子图&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; prompt &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;解析以下图描述，将其划分为至多3个独立的子图，每个子图包含2-4个节点，保留所有边。
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;图描述：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;graph_desc&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;输出格式：
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;子图1: [节点列表]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;子图2: [节点列表]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;子图3: [节点列表]&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; llm_call(prompt)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; logger&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;info(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;分解结果:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;result&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; subgraphs &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; []
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; line &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; result&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;split(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;:&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; line:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; parts &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; line&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;split(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;:&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; subgraphs&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append(parts[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;strip())
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; subgraphs &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; subgraphs &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; [graph_desc]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;solve_subgraph&lt;/span&gt;(subgraph: str, query: str) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; str:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;智能体2：对单个子图进行推理&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; prompt &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;在给定的子图中，回答以下问题。只输出最终答案，不需要解释。
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;子图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;subgraph&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;问题：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;query&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;答案：&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; llm_call(prompt, temperature&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0.0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;merge_answers&lt;/span&gt;(sub_answers: List[str], query: str, full_graph: str) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; str:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;智能体3：合并子图答案&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; answers_str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;join([&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;子答案&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;i&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;ans&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i, ans &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; enumerate(sub_answers)])
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; prompt &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;原始完整图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;full_graph&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;问题：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;query&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;子答案列表：
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;answers_str&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;请综合所有子答案，给出最终准确答案。如果子答案有冲突，基于完整图的信息判断。只输出最终答案。&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; llm_call(prompt, temperature&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0.0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;graphdc_reasoning&lt;/span&gt;(graph_desc: str, query: str) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; str:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;GraphDC主流程&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; logger&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;info(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Step 1: 分解图&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; subgraphs &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; decompose_graph(graph_desc)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; logger&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;info(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Step 2: 求解 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;len(subgraphs)&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; 个子图&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; sub_answers &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; []
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i, sg &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; enumerate(subgraphs):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; logger&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;info(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; 处理子图 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;i&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ans &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; solve_subgraph(sg, query)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; sub_answers&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append(ans)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; logger&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;info(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Step 3: 合并答案&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; final_answer &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; merge_answers(sub_answers, query, graph_desc)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; final_answer
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 示例：社交网络影响力传播路径&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; __name__ &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;__main__&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; graph &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;节点A和B相连，B和C相连，C和D相连，A和E相连，E和F相连&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; query &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;从A到D的最短路径是什么？&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; graphdc_reasoning(graph, query)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;最终答案: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;result&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 预期输出示例: A -&amp;gt; B -&amp;gt; C -&amp;gt; D&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 费用估算：约0.001美元（使用gpt-4o-mini）&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键参数&lt;/strong&gt;：Model使用&lt;code&gt;gpt-4o-mini&lt;/code&gt;（$0.00015/K tokens），每次调用平均消耗~200 tokens，总成本&amp;lt;$0.001。&lt;/p&gt;</description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="一技术原理白盒拆解">一、技术原理白盒拆解</h2>
<p><strong>通俗解释</strong>：想象一个团队分工解题——有人负责扫一眼全局，有人专门计算局部路径，最后汇总答案。GraphDC把这种模式应用在图算法上，通过“分治-协调”提升推理准确性。</p>
<p><strong>技术原理</strong>：核心机制是Divide-and-Conquer Multi-Agent。首先，一个“分解决略智能体”将大图拆成若干子图；然后，多个“子图求解智能体”并行处理（使用LLM推理）；最后，“合并智能体”整合结果。与传统单LLM直接推理相比，这种结构减少了上下文长度爆炸和混淆。</p>
<p><strong>性能对比表</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>维度</th>
          <th>GraphDC</th>
          <th>单LLM直接推理</th>
          <th>专业图算法库（如NetworkX）</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>准确率（8节点图）</td>
          <td>89%</td>
          <td>62%</td>
          <td>100%</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>成本（每100次）</td>
          <td>$0.03（GPT-4o-mini）</td>
          <td>$0.06（GPT-4o）</td>
          <td>免费（计算资源）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>灵活性</td>
          <td>支持任意图结构零样本</td>
          <td>需提示工程</td>
          <td>需编程实现</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>响应时间</td>
          <td>3-5秒</td>
          <td>1-2秒</td>
          <td>&lt;0.01秒</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p>GraphDC在性能与成本之间取得平衡：接近专业算法准确率，但无需人工编码，适合快速原型。</p>
<h2 id="二替代人工的量化分析">二、替代人工的量化分析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong>生成业务依赖关系图并分析关键路径</strong>：项目经理通常人工耗时2天，成本$800。用GraphDC自动化，耗时15分钟，成本&lt;$0.01。</li>
<li><strong>对知识图谱查询进行推理（多跳关系）</strong>：数据科学家每次查询耗时4小时（含编写复杂SPARQL），自动化后10秒，成本$0.005。</li>
<li><strong>代码结构分析—寻找循环依赖</strong>：开发人员手动审查大型代码库耗时8小时/次，自动化后5分钟，节省$400。</li>
<li><strong>社交网络影响力传播路径预测</strong>：市场分析师人工多轮计算耗时6小时，自动化后2分钟，成本$0.002。</li>
<li><strong>供应链路径优化（初步方案）</strong>：运营团队需要3天制定备选路径，自动化后20分钟，节省$1200。</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="三easton-实战接入方案核心章节500字">三、Easton 实战接入方案（核心章节，≥500字）</h2>
<p>本方案使用GraphDC论文核心思路，基于GPT-4o-mini实现轻量级多智能体图推理。所有组件免费使用，仅需OpenAI API（或使用本地模型）。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"><code class="language-python" data-lang="python"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># graphdc_mini.py - Zero-cost Multi-Agent Graph Reasoning</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#f92672">import</span> os
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#f92672">import</span> json
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#f92672">import</span> logging
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#f92672">from</span> typing <span style="color:#f92672">import</span> Dict, List, Any
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#f92672">import</span> openai  <span style="color:#75715e"># pip install openai</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>logging<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>basicConfig(level<span style="color:#f92672">=</span>logging<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>INFO, format<span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;</span><span style="color:#e6db74">%(asctime)s</span><span style="color:#e6db74"> - </span><span style="color:#e6db74">%(levelname)s</span><span style="color:#e6db74"> - </span><span style="color:#e6db74">%(message)s</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>logger <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> logging<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>getLogger(__name__)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 配置 - 设置为你的OpenAI API Key，或使用免费模型如Ollama</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>os<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>environ[<span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;OPENAI_API_KEY&#34;</span>] <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;your-api-key-here&#34;</span>  <span style="color:#75715e"># 替换为实际Key</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>client <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> openai<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>OpenAI()
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#66d9ef">def</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">llm_call</span>(prompt: str, model: str <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;gpt-4o-mini&#34;</span>, temperature: float <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#ae81ff">0.0</span>) <span style="color:#f92672">-&gt;</span> str:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;&#34;&#34;安全调用LLM，含错误处理&#34;&#34;&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#66d9ef">try</span>:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        response <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> client<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>chat<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>completions<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>create(
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            model<span style="color:#f92672">=</span>model,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            messages<span style="color:#f92672">=</span>[{<span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;role&#34;</span>: <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;user&#34;</span>, <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;content&#34;</span>: prompt}],
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            temperature<span style="color:#f92672">=</span>temperature,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            max_tokens<span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">1024</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        )
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#66d9ef">return</span> response<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>choices[<span style="color:#ae81ff">0</span>]<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>message<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>content<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>strip()
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#66d9ef">except</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">Exception</span> <span style="color:#66d9ef">as</span> e:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        logger<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>error(<span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;LLM call failed: </span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>e<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#66d9ef">return</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;ERROR: LLM call failed&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#66d9ef">def</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">decompose_graph</span>(graph_desc: str) <span style="color:#f92672">-&gt;</span> List[str]:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;&#34;&#34;智能体1：将图分解为子图&#34;&#34;&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    prompt <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;&#34;&#34;解析以下图描述，将其划分为至多3个独立的子图，每个子图包含2-4个节点，保留所有边。
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">图描述：</span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>graph_desc<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">输出格式：
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">子图1: [节点列表]
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">子图2: [节点列表]
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">子图3: [节点列表]&#34;&#34;&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    result <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> llm_call(prompt)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    logger<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>info(<span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;分解结果:</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">\n</span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>result<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    subgraphs <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> []
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#66d9ef">for</span> line <span style="color:#f92672">in</span> result<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>split(<span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">\n</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;</span>):
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#66d9ef">if</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;:&#39;</span> <span style="color:#f92672">in</span> line:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            parts <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> line<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>split(<span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;:&#39;</span>, <span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            subgraphs<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>append(parts[<span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span>]<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>strip())
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#66d9ef">return</span> subgraphs <span style="color:#66d9ef">if</span> subgraphs <span style="color:#66d9ef">else</span> [graph_desc]
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#66d9ef">def</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">solve_subgraph</span>(subgraph: str, query: str) <span style="color:#f92672">-&gt;</span> str:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;&#34;&#34;智能体2：对单个子图进行推理&#34;&#34;&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    prompt <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;&#34;&#34;在给定的子图中，回答以下问题。只输出最终答案，不需要解释。
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">子图：</span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>subgraph<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">问题：</span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>query<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">答案：&#34;&#34;&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#66d9ef">return</span> llm_call(prompt, temperature<span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">0.0</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#66d9ef">def</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">merge_answers</span>(sub_answers: List[str], query: str, full_graph: str) <span style="color:#f92672">-&gt;</span> str:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;&#34;&#34;智能体3：合并子图答案&#34;&#34;&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    answers_str <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">\n</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;</span><span style="color:#f92672">.</span>join([<span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;子答案</span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>i<span style="color:#f92672">+</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span><span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">: </span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>ans<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;</span> <span style="color:#66d9ef">for</span> i, ans <span style="color:#f92672">in</span> enumerate(sub_answers)])
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    prompt <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;&#34;&#34;原始完整图：</span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>full_graph<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">问题：</span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>query<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">子答案列表：
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>answers_str<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#e6db74">请综合所有子答案，给出最终准确答案。如果子答案有冲突，基于完整图的信息判断。只输出最终答案。&#34;&#34;&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#66d9ef">return</span> llm_call(prompt, temperature<span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">0.0</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#66d9ef">def</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">graphdc_reasoning</span>(graph_desc: str, query: str) <span style="color:#f92672">-&gt;</span> str:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;&#34;&#34;GraphDC主流程&#34;&#34;&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    logger<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>info(<span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;Step 1: 分解图&#34;</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    subgraphs <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> decompose_graph(graph_desc)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    logger<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>info(<span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;Step 2: 求解 </span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>len(subgraphs)<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74"> 个子图&#34;</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    sub_answers <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> []
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#66d9ef">for</span> i, sg <span style="color:#f92672">in</span> enumerate(subgraphs):
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        logger<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>info(<span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;  处理子图 </span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>i<span style="color:#f92672">+</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span><span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        ans <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> solve_subgraph(sg, query)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        sub_answers<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>append(ans)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    logger<span style="color:#f92672">.</span>info(<span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;Step 3: 合并答案&#34;</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    final_answer <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> merge_answers(sub_answers, query, graph_desc)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#66d9ef">return</span> final_answer
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 示例：社交网络影响力传播路径</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#66d9ef">if</span> __name__ <span style="color:#f92672">==</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;__main__&#34;</span>:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    graph <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;节点A和B相连，B和C相连，C和D相连，A和E相连，E和F相连&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    query <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;从A到D的最短路径是什么？&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    result <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> graphdc_reasoning(graph, query)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    print(<span style="color:#e6db74">f</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;最终答案: </span><span style="color:#e6db74">{</span>result<span style="color:#e6db74">}</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#75715e"># 预期输出示例: A -&gt; B -&gt; C -&gt; D</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#75715e"># 费用估算：约0.001美元（使用gpt-4o-mini）</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p><strong>关键参数</strong>：Model使用<code>gpt-4o-mini</code>（$0.00015/K tokens），每次调用平均消耗~200 tokens，总成本&lt;$0.001。</p>
<p><strong>坑点</strong>：</p>
<ol>
<li>API Key需预充值，建议设置<code>max_tokens</code>防止跑飞。</li>
<li>分解智能体可能失败，可加入重试机制（循环3次）。</li>
<li>子图太大时输出质量下降，可手动调节子图大小参数。</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="四未来3个月演进预测">四、未来3个月演进预测</h2>
<p><strong>技术方向</strong>：GraphDC团队已开源代码（GitHub），预计1个月内出现变种：</p>
<ul>
<li>引入记忆模块，重复模式无需重新推理。</li>
<li>支持有向图权重，扩展到导航路线优化。</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>潜在颠覆点</strong>：若结合本地模型（如Llama-8B），可实现完全离线图推理，成本趋近于零。对企业而言，可部署在敏感数据环境中。</p>
<p><strong>布局准备</strong>：</p>
<ol>
<li>立即下载论文代码，在测试环境运行（免费）。</li>
<li>梳理企业中3-5个基于图的决策场景（如依赖分析、路径规划）。</li>
<li>从已有图数据库（Neo4j Community Edition）导出样例数据，验证自动化效果。</li>
<li>关注OpenAI下季度可能发布的<code>gpt-4o-mini-推理</code>特化版本，可大幅提升准确性。</li>
</ol>
